       <div class="singlepost"> 
        <div class="post" id="post-main-93031"> 
         <div class="entry"> 
          <h1 class="post-title single"><a href="http://blogs.kqed.org/bayareabites/2015/02/13/bittman-does-berkeley-talking-food-politics-with-mark-bittman/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Bittman Does Berkeley: Talking Food Politics With Mark Bittman">Bittman Does Berkeley: Talking Food Politics With Mark Bittman</a></h1> 
          <div class="meta single"> 
           <span class="meta-author"> <a href="http://blogs.kqed.org/bayareabites/author/shelbypope/" title="Posts by Shelby Pope" rel="author">Shelby Pope</a> | </span> 
           <span class="meta-date"> February 13, 2015 </span> 
           <span class="meta-comments"> | <a href="http://blogs.kqed.org/bayareabites/2015/02/13/bittman-does-berkeley-talking-food-politics-with-mark-bittman/#comments" rel="bookmark" title="Comments for Bittman Does Berkeley: Talking Food Politics With Mark Bittman"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="93031 http://blogs.kqed.org/bayareabites/?p=93031">2 Comments</span></a> </span> 
          </div> 
          <div class="articletools"> 
           <ul class="meta-gestures"> 
            <li class="meta-print">
             <div class="printfriendly pf-alignleft">
              <a href="http://www.printfriendly.com/print?url=http%3A%2F%2Fblogs.kqed.org%2Fbayareabites%2F2015%2F02%2F13%2Fbittman-does-berkeley-talking-food-politics-with-mark-bittman%2F" rel="nofollow" onclick="window.print(); return false;"><img style="border:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none; box-shadow:none;margin-right:4px;" src="http://cdn.printfriendly.com/pf-icon-small.gif" alt="PrintFriendly and PDF" width="18" height="18"><span class="printfriendly-text2">Print</span></a>
             </div></li> 
            <li class="meta-comments"><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://blogs.kqed.org/bayareabites/2015/02/13/bittman-does-berkeley-talking-food-politics-with-mark-bittman/#comments" title="Comment on Bittman Does Berkeley: Talking Food Politics With Mark Bittman"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="93031 http://blogs.kqed.org/bayareabites/?p=93031"> <strong>2</strong> Comments</span></a></span></li> 
            <li class="twitter"> <a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-via="bayareabites">Tweet</a> <script>!function(d,s,id){var js,fjs=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];if(!d.getElementById(id)){js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;js.src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js";fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js,fjs);}}(document,"script","twitter-wjs");</script> </li> 
            <li class="fb"> 
             <div id="fb-root"></div> <script>(function(d, s, id) {
