         <h3 class="widgettitle"><span><a href="http://blogs.kqed.org/bayareabites/category/guides-2/">BAB GUIDES</a></span></h3>
         <div class="cat-posts-widget textwidget"> 
          <div class="post"> 
           <div class="entry clearfix"> 
            <a href="http://blogs.kqed.org/bayareabites/2015/02/07/bay-area-bites-guide-to-5-movie-theaters-serving-food-and-alcoholic-beverages/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Bay Area Bites Guide To 5 Movie Theaters Serving Food and Alcoholic Beverages"> <img class="thumbnail" src="http://blogs.kqed.org/bayareabites/files/2015/02/featured2-288x162.jpg" alt="Bay Area Bites Guide To 5 Movie Theaters Serving Food and Alcoholic Beverages" title="Bay Area Bites Guide To 5 Movie Theaters Serving Food and Alcoholic Beverages"> </a> 
            <p class="post-title"><a href="http://blogs.kqed.org/bayareabites/2015/02/07/bay-area-bites-guide-to-5-movie-theaters-serving-food-and-alcoholic-beverages/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Bay Area Bites Guide To 5 Movie Theaters Serving Food and Alcoholic Beverages">Bay Area Bites Guide To 5 Movie Theaters Serving Food and Alcoholic Beverages</a></p> 
            <p>Date night just got easier with this list of five local theaters that serve more than just popcorn and Junior Mints.</p> 
           </div> 
           <div class="meta single"> 
            <span class="meta-author"> <a href="http://blogs.kqed.org/bayareabites/author/shelbypope/" title="Posts by Shelby Pope" rel="author">Shelby Pope</a> | </span> 
