            <span class="meta-comments"> | <a href="http://blogs.kqed.org/bayareabites/2014/11/17/bay-area-bites-guide-to-8-exceptional-east-bay-japanese-izakayas/#comments" rel="bookmark" title="Comments for Bay Area Bites Guide to 8 Exceptional Japanese Izakayas in the East Bay"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="82746 http://blogs.kqed.org/bayareabites/?p=82746">5 Comments</span></a> </span> 
